name: Zeus
description: Zeus is a delightful character in the whimsical world of Pepe the Frog. He is inspired by the talented artist Matt Furie. Zeus is no ordinary canine. He serves as Matt’s alter ego within the Pepe universe, embodying Matt’s unique perspective on life. As Pepe’s dog and sidekick, he stands out with his one of a kind earring and a rainbow colored tongue that spreads joy to everyone that he comes across.
